casebody.data:
APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2014-0353. In re R.W.

Hamilton App. Nos. C-130151 and C-130152, 2014-Ohio-175. Discretionary appeal accepted; cause held for the decision in 2013-0579, In re D.M., 1st Dist. Hamilton No. C-120794, 2013-Ohio-668; and briefing schedule stayed.

O’Connor, C.J., and O’Donnell and French, JJ., would accept the appeal on Proposition of Law No. I only.
